ZH: 他告诉我一个吓慌的故事。
EN: He told me a terrifying story.
ZH: 我开车的时候，突然有只猫跳了出来，吓慌了我。
EN: While I was driving, a cat suddenly jumped out, scaring me to death.
ZH: 昨天晚上，我看了一部吓慌人的恐怖电影。
EN: Last night, I watched a really scary horror movie.
ZH: 我的弟弟害怕鬼故事，所以每次听到就会吓慌。
EN: My little brother is afraid of ghost stories, so he gets scared every time he hears one.
ZH: 他看到那只巨大的蜘蛛时，吓慌了。
EN: He got scared when he saw that giant spider.
ZH: 她的尖叫吓慌了我。
EN: Her scream scared the hell out of me.
ZH: 我没想到他突然拍了我一下，吓慌了我。
EN: I didn't expect him to suddenly slap me, it scared the living daylights out of me.
ZH: 这个悬崖上的小路很吓慌人。
EN: This narrow path on the cliff is really terrifying.
ZH: 昨天晚上发生的事情真的让我吓慌了一跳。
EN: What happened last night really shocked me.
ZH: 她不小心把手划伤了，吓慌了。
EN: She accidentally cut her hand and got a fright.
ZH: 他看到蟑螂时忍不住吓慌了。
EN: He couldn't help but get scared when he saw the cockroach.
ZH: 考试之前我总是会吓慌，害怕不及格。
EN: I always get scared before exams, afraid of failing.
