EN: The magician's performance was too frightening.
ZH: 我的弟弟被爸爸的突然大喊吓慌了。
EN: My little brother got scared when dad suddenly shouted.
ZH: 在深夜里听到的那声巨响把我们吓慌了。
EN: The loud noise we heard in the middle of the night scared us to death.
ZH: 环境氛围太恐怖了，吓慌我了。
EN: The atmosphere was too horrifying, it scared me.
ZH: 看到他的表情，我吓慌了。
EN: I got scared when I saw his expression.
ZH: 他好像看到了什么吓慌人的东西。
EN: He seemed to have seen something terrifying.
ZH: 他吓慌了一大跳，因为有人突然敲了门。
EN: He got a big fright because someone suddenly knocked on the door.
